# Keep `gcloud builds submit` uploads lean. gcloud honors .gitignore by default, but
# NOT .git itself or .dockerignore-only excludes — enumerate them here. The docker
# build step inside Cloud Build still applies .dockerignore (so apps/ etc. are stripped
# from the image COPY); this file only governs what gets uploaded as the build context.
.git
**/node_modules
infra/cdk.out
infra-gcp/bin
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
.claude
*.log
cdk.out
